## A Brief Introduction to Emigrant City

### Our Goal

To extract structured data from over 6,000 handwritten mortgage and bond ledgers from the Emigrant Savings Bank records.

To divide the labor -- and to help ensure accuracy -- we've broken the work into 3 free-standing tasks. These tasks follow a sequence, but they can be performed independently (feel free to focus on the one you enjoy best).

### Task 1: Mark

Here you'll be identifying various pieces of information on the page. You won't be typing, just drawing boxes. This helps plot a route for the transcribers in Task 2. You may see existing marks left by other users. Just pick up where they left off.

