### Task 2: Transcribe

Here you'll type out the words and numbers inside the fields marked by your fellow volunteers. Heads up: there may be some tricky handwriting to decipher! But don't worry, we'll get these transcribed multiple times to ensure accuracy, so give it your best shot and move on.

