### Task 3: Verify

Every document will be transcribed several times by multiple volunteers, and our software looks for agreement among them. If a field has been transcribed consistently and independently three times, it has reached "consensus" and is added to the final data set. If there are conflicting entries, those are queued up in the Verify task, where you can vote on the most accurate transcription, or, if needed, add your own.

